title: Duck Commander: Duck Defense (Duck Dynasty) v1.0.0 [+OBB] Androi
description:
This time, the Robertson Duckmen are forced to defend their Louisiana land and Miss KayÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fine baked goods from wildlife-turned-enemies. Play as Willie, Phil, Si and Jase Robertson in this Tower Defense style game as they use a variety of duck blinds, duck calls and redneck ingenuity to push back against the high-powered enemies that have rallied against them! Prove your worth to join the ranks of the Duck Commanders!
15 locales and levels: From the swamps to the forests of Louisiana, play through 15 levels in three environments that have new enemies crawling out of every nook and cranny.
Classic tower defense strategy: Defend your map from advancing enemies with three different tower types: duck blind, tree stand and ATV Garage.
Use over 40 tower upgrades: Enhance your towers with unique upgrades like hunting dogs, duck decoys and lightning rods. 
Rely on duck calls: Each Robertson has a unique duck call that affects enemies differently, including WillieÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Camo Max call that causes extra enemy damage.
Defend against wild enemies: Louisiana wildlife including ducks, squirrels, beavers, chipmunks riding frogs, robotic possums, mystical alligators and even powerful mechanical squirrel boss enemies. 
Get the edge: Earn or purchase currency to spend on power-ups you can use in-game, like an explosive Propane Tank that clears the map of enemies.
Choose your own difficulty: Three difficulty levels and an extra challenging mode will test every player.
Achievements: Earn achievements and find secrets hidden in each map!
Endless Mode: Three endless mode maps pit you against the endless waves of bad guys. See how long you can survive, then post it to the leaderboards!
Required Android O/S : 4.0+
